                              двухстрочная надпись, буквы обведены красной краской.</p>
                           <p xml:lang="en">Stele adorned with a moulded cornice. Broken off on the bottom. The front and sides are plastered. Below the cornice: two-line inscription is cut 
                           and traced in red paint.</p>
